# TaskForge 🔧

A simple and powerful CLI tool to manage your daily tasks efficiently.

## 🚀 Features

* Add new tasks
* List all tasks
* Mark tasks as completed
* Delete tasks
* Persistent local storage using JSON

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/taskforge.git
cd taskforge
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## ▶️ Usage

```bash
python taskforge.py add "Learn Python"
python taskforge.py list
python taskforge.py done 1
python taskforge.py delete 1
```

